# Plan Gate Check — Orschell Excavating E-Commerce Full-Stack

## Evaluation

### Research completeness
- Planner explicitly states "All 5 research questions answered" with STATUS: READY.
- Brand confirmed via orschellx.com: dark steel palette, construction orange #F76B10, Barlow Condensed / Inter fonts, rugged industrial identity — all with exact hex values.
- Product taxonomy confirmed against real Orschell merch store: 20 real/realistic products across 5 categories with names, SKUs, prices, stock counts.
- Clone source named and rationale given (adverteyes Express+TS+JWT pattern, node:sqlite swap confirmed from CLAUDE.md).
- Package.json dependency versions pinned and confirmed.
- No unknowns flagged; all research questions closed.

### Requirement traceability
All 8 posting requirements mapped to concrete demo features:
- User auth + account management: JWT, register/login, account page, order history, 2 seeded accounts ✓
- Product catalog management: Admin CMS CRUD (22 endpoints) ✓
- Inventory tracking: Atomic decrement, low-stock flags, admin stock edits ✓
- Order processing workflows: Cart to checkout to confirmation, 4-state admin pipeline ✓
- Payment gateway: Mock checkout labeled "Demo / Mock Payment" ✓
- REST API development: 22 endpoints fully specified with HTTP methods + guards ✓
- Performance optimization: Paginated queries, 7 named indexes, client-side caching ✓
- Database improvements: Relational schema, FKs, CHECK constraints, seeds ✓

### Technical decisions sound
- `node:sqlite` (not `better-sqlite3`) — CLAUDE.md-confirmed safe on Windows Node 22 ✓
- Schema written Postgres-compatible; migration path documented for deck ✓
- Flask bridge pattern follows CLAUDE.md Surface runner conventions ✓
- Vite frontend builds to ~3 files; stays within demo file-count cap ✓
- Atomic inventory update prevents oversell without needing full transactions ✓

### Gaps or problems
None. Plan is complete, all assumptions backed by research, all risks have stated mitigations.
Minor: admin CMS is wide (4 panels); planner flagged it and prescribed tab routing — builder concern, not a plan gap.

VERDICT: pass

## handoff
- produced: gate check confirms plan is research-complete, all 8 requirements traceable, no open unknowns
- decisions: plan passes; no pre-researcher loop needed
- next needs: demo-builder — clone adverteyes backend, swap node:sqlite, build 22 endpoints, seed 20 products, build Vite+React frontend with construction-orange industrial design, register Surface service, write Flask bridge
- risks: frontend 12-file count is tight; builder should consolidate admin into tabbed single page as planner prescribed
